    "text": "Shih Chien University\nEnglish Taught Program in International Business\n\n\nStatistics I & II\n\n\nUndergraduate, Fall, 2024, 2025; Spring, 2025, 2026.\n\n\nA two-semester introduction to statistical reasoning, covering descriptive statistics, probability, and inference through hypothesis testing, regression, and ANOVA. Each week pairs a concept lecture with a hands-on lab session.\n\n\nCourse site\n\n\n\n\nProgramming for Application\n\n\nUndergraduate, Spring, 2024, 2025, 2026.\n\n\nAn introduction to programming fundamentals in R, emphasizing how to translate practical business and data problems into working code through weekly in-class exercises.\n\n\nCourse site\n\n\n\n\nData Analysis\n\n\nUndergraduate, Fall, 2024, 2025.\n\n\nPractical data analysis and communication in the modern R ecosystem, centered on the grammar of graphics and data visualization with ggplot2, turning analytical findings into clear visual narratives.\n\n\nCourse site"
